        "text_hTDcNJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h5>PRACTICAL AND PORTABLE</h5><p>The biggest advantage of choosing an inflatable iSUP for your water adventures, means once deflated, the board can be easily rolled up and packed away with all its accessories for travel by car or plane.</p><h5>STRONG AND RIGID</h5><p>Inflatable paddle boards gain their strength and rigidity as they inflate, the boards drop stitch construction provides both strength and stiffness as well as keeping the iSUP super lightweight for effortless paddling and carrying in and out of the water.</p><h5>SUPERIOR COMFORT AND SUPPORT</h5><p>Inflatable paddle boards are designed with a softer deck, to offer a more comfortable and relaxed experience for your feet, the cushioned support also has many benefits for your knees, back, and neck.</p><h5>WHICH PADDLE BOARD?</h5><p>Our iSUP collections here at Wave are split into 5 key categories, covering beginners, kids and surfers, family friendly all-rounders, intermediate skill level boards and our Pro range of professional performance paddle boards.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-sm",
            "text_max_size": 32,
